						<div class="postbody">I think YY-CHR supports that display mode (0,1,2,3 for 16x16).  I know that's what I use for my metatiles (makes a lot of sense, especially for animating metatiles in CHR-RAM).
<br />
<br /><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">But with metatiles, wouldn't you have to like switch between increment 1 and 32?</div>
<br />
<br />Nope.  Each metatile is 2 nametable columns, so just render each nametable column seperately with 32 increment all the way down.</div>

